Webex App | Share link to your Personal Room
You can easily add your Personal Room link in a Webex App space for an instant meeting with some of the space members. Your Personal Room is convenient because itâ€™s always available and you never have to book it.
Your Personal Room must be associated with Webex App before you can add your Personal Room link to a message. See Webex App | Set up your Personal Room for more information.
When writing a message, select My Personal Room invite.
Your Personal Room link is inserted in the message. You don't have to type it. Here's an example: https://company.webex.com/meet/acassidy